dcterms:description: The GBOT dataset is exclusively a synthetic dataset designed for 6D object pose/tracking tasks. It comprises 3D printable assembly parts and contains five evaluation sequences, each presenting different levels of difficulty for object tracking (normal, dynamic, hand occlusion, and blur).
dcterms:title: GBOT Dataset

dcterms:creator: H. Schieber
S. Li
N. Corell
D. Roth
dcterms:description: The ASDF dataset provides ground truth annotations for 6D object poses and assembly states of 3D printing parts. It includes four distinct assembly parts and varying numbers of images.
dcterms:title: ASDF Dataset
